{"tid":17404,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［世紀選擇題］有女朋友唔該入一入黎","createTime":"2016-12-01T21:12:43.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T05:23:16.000Z","uid":48606,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"37c0b7c8158ab68797240f7fba0f540ef00464fc","tid":17404,"uid":48606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T21:12:43.000Z","msg":"我有兩個朋友今年都係23歲 <br />\n一個12月bachelor畢業 ，女朋友大距兩年，大陸妹<br />\n一個已經讀完bachelor 依家讀緊一個certificate 準備4月讀完，女朋友細距一年，台灣妹<br />\n依排距地女朋友都話要讀完書就結婚<br />\n男方們雖然屋企有d家底<br />\n但係男方們都未有任何經濟能力<br />\n女方們都話一係讀完結婚一係分手<br />\n<br />\n請問各位巴打點拆彈！"},{"pid":"e6b5d1868aaff9039abdacae73d47b68c16e82c5","tid":17404,"uid":27919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T21:21:42.000Z","msg":"讀完書工都未搵到撚有錢結婚呀<br />\n<br />\n結婚嘅錢都冇啦<br />\n<br />\n到時又攤長雙手問老豆老母拎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n女人永遠都唔會明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac3119863afb03d0d5761630fa3a2666b11a1cf3","tid":17404,"uid":15946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T21:23:20.000Z","msg":"可唔可以問下點解要咁心急？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b76ade0d318ce388d4ee2362cb51860a7ee163f","tid":17404,"uid":33037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T21:24:07.000Z","msg":"答佢:結你老母"},{"pid":"ac4e2e2e1d728b22756fb65d854338c4f4fc953f","tid":17404,"uid":48606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T21:24:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>讀完書工都未搵到撚有錢結婚呀<br />\n<br />\n結婚嘅錢都冇啦<br />\n<br />\n到時又攤長雙手問老豆老母拎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n女人永遠都唔會明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就係！你話結左婚同沒結婚有咩分別！唔通生個仔出黎，又叫父母養。父母肯啊，你都無面啦"},{"pid":"b03de5db5454e3bbb2d7d0766d86c5bb6bcf041f","tid":17404,"uid":48606,"like":0